OL,3,CPrince of Wales remembers Diana on
OL,4,CMother's Day
OL,6,FThe Prince of Wales said he remembers
OL,7,Fhis late mother Diana, Princess of
OL,8,FWales "today and every day" as he
OL,9,Fshared a photograph of them together
OL,10,Fto mark Mother's Day.
OL,12,FThe picture, posted online for the
OL,13,Ffirst time from the family's private
OL,14,Fcollection, shows Diana with a two-
OL,15,Fyear-old William in a field of
OL,16,Fflowers, taken at the family's main
OL,17,Fhome at Highgrove, Gloucestershire, in
OL,18,F1984.
