OL,3,CPrince of Wales remembers Diana on
OL,4,CMother's Day
OL,6,FWilliam's signed message, posted on
OL,7,Fsocial media site X, said:
OL,8,F"Remembering my mother, today and
OL,9,Fevery day. Thinking of all those who
OL,10,Fare remembering someone they love
OL,11,Ftoday. Happy Mother's Day. W"
OL,13,FDiana, who died aged 36 following a
OL,14,Froad accident in Paris on August 31
OL,15,F1997, would have turned 65 on July 1
OL,16,Fthis year.
OL,18,FThe royal family also posted a
OL,19,Fselection of photos on X to mark
OL,20,FMother's Day.
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@]O]
