OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773691869
OL,3,CPrince of Wales remembers Diana on
OL,4,CMother's Day
OL,6,FThey included a photo of the King and
OL,7,Fhis sister Anne, now the Princess
OL,8,FRoyal, at Balmoral, Scotland, in 1953
OL,9,Fwith their mother, the late Queen
OL,10,FElizabeth II.
OL,12,FThe family are seated on a garden
OL,13,Fbench with the Queen's corgi, Sue, in
OL,14,Fthe background.
OL,16,FThe photograph was taken before the
OL,17,Fbirths of Charles' younger brothers,
OL,18,FAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor and Edward,
OL,19,Fnow the Duke of Edinburgh.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
